{"tid":212412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王振民指未來5年不適合重啟政改：普選會像中東內戰內亂","createTime":"2017-04-22T11:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T13:24:29.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e22f36c4a12193b0a2860635b78443f2f788fa9f","tid":212412,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">王振民指未來5年不適合重啟政改：普選會像中東內戰內亂<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170422/s00001/d09ed1609118ae47b868a99b32ff9ee7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170422%2Fs00001%2Fd09ed1609118ae47b868a99b32ff9ee7.jpg&h=7450a5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦法律部長王振民在北京表示，香港未來5年不適合重啟政改。<br />\n<br />\n王振民稱，過去花了多年時間處理政改卻都不成功，不能把未來5年、10年時間都用來處理政改而不解決經濟民生等問題，「你覺得我們就別的事都不幹了，都處理政改嗎？我覺得我們不可能同時做那麼多事情」。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，現時香港社會撕裂主因是經濟民生發展問題沒有解決，「不是說一政改就把這些問題解決了」。<br />\n<br />\n王振民之後稱，全世界很多國家把時間用作搞民主，結果是像中東等地，「普選以後結果都是內戰內亂，天天都產生那麼多難民到世界各地，這都是政改造成的，都是搞普選造成這麼一個結果」，反問記者「你們希望香港是這樣嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否對候任特首林鄭月娥沒有信心，王振民說，相信林鄭月娥是出色及成功的特首，對她寄予厚望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170422/s00001/1492845612212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170422%2Fs00001%2F1492845612212&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a3abe89d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170422%2Fs00001%2F1492845612212&h=808f6c67\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170422/s00001/1492845612212</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班中國奴才"},{"pid":"2e0bd8d2be80cd5580f2578006d5328c95466f47","tid":212412,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n<br />\n香港人民智味開發<br />\n<br />\n普咩撚野選<br />\n<br />\n華人是要管的<br />\n<br />\n5000年不變"},{"pid":"b90604ade772ae33222906914cc73e49db05ce11","tid":212412,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1dcb34d21f51632ceac1a657758b5bbad7a6160","tid":212412,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"會內戰?乜咁睇得起香港人"},{"pid":"775750f1108f91eec296614a03f311d374c6b192","tid":212412,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"九龍打新界？定係深圳打香港"},{"pid":"a68009dde072a5fd8dcd6b6e9cdf67d4e99f529e","tid":212412,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"支那狗會講信用咩<br />\n搵班五毛狗上來轉移視線就得"},{"pid":"59a5ea6f864d6250109d218436bcec402f3a1b85","tid":212412,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"普選會內亂？<br />\n戇鳩， 根本冇根據， 記者戇鳩鳩唔問佢點推斷出來"},{"pid":"722b60a2268505961ffc9c2a8af54620c1a76f21","tid":212412,"uid":34785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"美國係民主國家有無難民"},{"pid":"c03e93b0de90f939627366ad733deebec2faca69","tid":212412,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"Captain Hong Kong :civil war <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78daeb39553dd0657a2ba5810d50860b68203f1","tid":212412,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,